ent"," overall","."," Therefore"," there"," exists"," a"," need"," for"," a"," highly"," scalable"," distributed"," architecture"," capable"," of"," dealing"," with"," large"," numbers"," of"," simultaneous"," tasks"," without"," the"," drawbacks"," associated"," with"," conventional"," systems"],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"opt_1.3b","label":1}